msgid "steam-powered"
msgstr "steam-powered"

#: ../../S/steam-powered.rst:7
msgid "adj\\."
msgstr "形容詞"

#: ../../S/steam-powered.rst:9
msgid ""
"Old-fashioned or underpowered; archaic. This term does not have a strong "
"negative loading and may even be used semi-affectionately for something that"
" clanks and wheezes a lot but hangs in there doing the job."
msgstr ""
"旧式、または非力。古風。この用語は強い否定的な含みを持たず、がたがた音を立ててあえぎながらも仕事をこなし続ける何かに、半ば愛情を込めて使われることすらある。"
